{"tid":640581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夜歸女屯門遭南亞賊搶金頸鏈　人財兩傷","createTime":"2018-04-24T11:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T12:31:58.000Z","uid":173208,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8d1c1f1b8dfbd303c4a25e8c7f91d924affc6b05","tid":640581,"uid":173208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"南亞賊屯門搶劫夜歸女。凌晨1時許，一名姓周(43歲)女子，沿屯富路步向一條通往兆康苑的行人天橋返家，至名賢居對開，一名南亞男子突從後撲出，將女事主推跌在地，趁機搶去其戴在頸上一條約值2,000港元的金鏈，得手後逃走。女事主頸部留有紅痕，負傷返抵家門，將事件告知家人，由姓邱(51歲)男親友代為報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場調查，並於案發現場一帶兜截，暫時無發現。女事主其後由救護車送院治理。警方將案列作行劫，交由屯門警區刑事調查隊第3隊跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180424/bkn-20180424035431271-0424_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180424%2Fbkn-20180424035431271-0424_00822_001.html&d=PIhFHYhkq2G3Nufb4QOKIf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=fe16aee4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180424/bkn-20180424035431271-0424_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4efabda73ed7074e7990bf9cf6baa2dbee3a0b78","tid":640581,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"女事主好慘<br />\n一定好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003e4c249ca37ac21f1eac5489cc07e6f976ecac","tid":640581,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"冇失身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95208847f059d54e99ed0f2698a553519ae7adbf","tid":640581,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"003e4c249ca37ac21f1eac5489cc07e6f976ecac","tid":640581,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"冇失身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"